quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  2,72,Vi killed anim tiam disput yourselves. DI est expose ki VI PEN conceal
  2,73,Ni dir Strik (viktim) part heifer.) Ke when DI brought viktim dors life montr vi His sign ti vi kompren
  2,74,Despite this your kor hard like rok eben harder tie est rok river sxpruc out. Others krak release gentle streams ali rok cringe reverence DI! DI EST NENIAM unaware DE anything VI do
  2,75,Vi expect them kred as vi do when kelk da them uz auxd vort DI tiam distort gxi plen kompren thereof deliberately
  2,76,Kaj when ili meet believers ili dir Ni kred when ili get together each ali ili dir ne inform (believers) information don al vi DI lest vi proviz them support por their argument your Lord Vi ne kompren
  2,77,Ili ne kon ke DI kon cxio ili conceal cxio ili deklar
  2,78,Among them est gentiles ne kon scripture hearsay tiam assume ti ili kon gxi
  2,79,Do ve al those distort scripture their own man tiam dir This est ki DI revealed streb cheap sxtof gajn! Ve al them por such distortion ve al them por their illicit gajn
  2,80,Kelk dir Infer ne tusx us lim numer tag. Dir Hav vi pren such pledge DI! - DI NENIAM ROMP His pledge - Vi dir DI ki vi ne kon
  2,81,Ja those earn pek igx surrounded their evil work est dwellers Infer; ili abide gxi forever
  2,82,As por those kred plumb righteous life ili est dwellers Paradise; ili abide gxi forever